// ToastContainer
// Fixed container that renders all active toast notifications.
// Positioned at bottom-right of the viewport. Shows at most 5 toasts at once
// (the most recent). Stacks newest at the bottom via flex-col-reverse.

FUNCTION ToastContainer() -> JSX                                       EXPORT
  CALLS: Toast (Toast)
  Reads toasts from notificationStore.
  Takes the last 5 toasts (visibleToasts).
  Renders each as a Toast component with removeToast as the onDismiss callback.
  Container uses pointer-events-none so only the Toast buttons are interactive.
